node.text:
See you at Robson Square today - Repost from @oldgrowthvancity
•
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
On Friday May 21 Vancouver shows up to stand in solidarity with land defenders at Fairy Creek. We gather on the unceded territories of the xʷməθkʷəy̓əm (Musqueam), Sḵwx̱wú7mesh (Squamish), and səlilwətaɬ (Tsleil-Waututh) Nations.
⁠
We stand with Elder Bill Jones
We stand with Kati George-Jim⁠
We stand with Aya Clappis⁠
We stand with all front line defenders who have been holding it down for the past 9 months.⁠
⁠
We stand to end colonial violence and un-checked resource extraction within our last critical endangered ecosystems. ⁠
⁠
We stand against the RCMP's establishment of unlawful exclusion zones and against the tactics employed by the RCMP, BC NDP, and BC FORESTRY.⁠
⁠
We reject BC NDP, John Horgan's and BC Forestry's campaign of misinformation.⁠
⁠
FAIRY CREEK - CAYCUSE - WALBRAN ⁠
⁠
This is just the beginning.⁠
⁠
**Join us - May 21st - at the Courthouse - 2PM-6PM⁠**⁠

node.text:
Repost from @kenwukenwu
‘Last week I was fortunate to bring Nathalie Boltt @natboltt and her wonderful family, Phil her husband and Jupiter her son, on a tour of the amazing old-growth forests near Port Renfrew in Pacheedaht territory.

 Nathalie, who plays the evil villain Penelope Blossom in the hit series "Riverdale", has 2 million followers and has been a relentless champion for many years to protect old-growth forests in BC, and has worked to engage other celebrities in her circles to speak up.

 More photos and vids to come! 

Speak up to ensure the critical solutions to protect old-growth forests in BC at the link in my profile.’ … It was an absolute dream going on this adventure with Ken - and at a time of the worst heat wave in Canada that caused devastating wildfires, killing hundreds of people, thousands of animals, more forests…an untold toll of devastation for flora and fauna. Ask yourself - and your politicians- why are we allowing ancient forests, that absorb twice the amount of carbon compared to second growth forests, to be massacred for profit at this time of climate crisis? @johnhorgan4bc says he is doing ‘everything possible to stop wildfires’ - by enabling the logging of ancient trees for profit?! I urge you to speak up! Support @endangeredecosystemsalliance  as well as @fairycreekblockade  @thegreenparty_canada to halt old growth logging and negotiate  a new moratorium immediately. Now is the time. 🙏🏽- much love, Nat x 

#nathalieboltt #riverdale #colesprouse #markruffalo #bryanadams #leonardodicaprio #oldgrowth #ancientforest #bigtrees #endangeredecosystemsalliance #johnhorgan #katrineconroy
